	<FactionDef ParentName="FactionBase">
		<defName>DRG_Rough</defName>
		<label>Free Companies</label>
		<description>When their homeworld fell, not everyone wanted to start over. The harder elements of the displaced population broke from the civilian diaspora and kept moving. These were paramilitaries, security divisions, and opportunists with their formations intact.\n\nThey operate as free companies and bushwhacker bands, organized along the military lines they served under, selling their services where they can and taking what they want where they can't. They carry the same Imperial weapons as their settled cousins, but where the settlers see a finite supply to conserve, the Free Companies see a reason to keep raiding for spare parts and replacement gear.\n\nThey are not lawless chaos. They are something more dangerous: an army that lost its war and never demobilized.</description>
